## Overview

This file declares which focus groups are impacted by this concept and tracks approval status. Each impact becomes an approval requirement before implementation.

**Matrix-Based Approval:** Each impacted focus group independently reviews and approves. A concept is fully approved only when ALL required focus groups have approved.

