### Status Legend
- ⏳ Pending - Awaiting review
- ✅ Approved - Focus group approved
- 🚫 Rejected - Focus group rejected (see feedback)
- ⏸️ Blocked - Waiting on dependency

### SLA Legend
- ✓ On track
- ⚠️ Approaching deadline
- ⛔ Overdue

