## Approval Requirements

**Required for Implementation:**
- [ ] All impacted focus groups must approve (status = approved)
- [ ] No "Rejected" statuses (unless overridden)
- [ ] No "Blocked" statuses remaining
- [ ] Primary focus group approved

**Override Authority:**
Admins can force-approve blocked or pending approvals using `/wgsd override`. This creates an audit trail and notifies the original focus group.

